<p>
<lb n="1"/>Ārāmā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> namastuṁgga śiraḥ(ścuṁbbi) caṁdracāma 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>racārave <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> trailōkyanagarāraṁbha mūlastaṁbhāyaśaṁbhave <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="3"/>svasti śrī jayābhyudaya śālivāhana śakavaraṣaṁbbulu 
<lb n="4"/>1675 Agunēṭi śrīmukhanāma saṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Aṣāḍha śu 5 śukrāvāraṁ 
<lb n="5"/>hajarati Abdulakhādarakhānu nabābu sāhebulavā 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ri kumāruḍu hajaratiAbdulaganikhānusāhebu 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lavāru paragaṇe pasapula grāmānaku kōṭaku nayi 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>riti mūlana kaṭiṁccina buruju śilā śāsanaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī 
